In this article, Prime Minister Modi and President Trump express gratitude towards each other during a joint press conference. President Trump acknowledges the strong presence of Indian-Americans in the United States and highlights the progress made in trade, fighter jets, commercial airlines, energy, and other areas of cooperation. He also mentions the overwhelming support and enthusiasm shown by the Indian people during his visit to India. Prime Minister Modi responds but no translation is provided for his remarks. The press conference concludes with a thank you from President Trump to everyone present.